        public String getCNF2expression(List<String> positives,
                                List<String> negatives,
                                int numId,
                                String id)
        Parse a single conjunctive normal form (dimacs format) into a hlvl's expression sentence
        Parameters:
        positives - list of positive literals from the CNF expression
        negatives - list of negative literals from the CNF expression
        numId - string that represent a relation "r"
        id - index of the current relation in the hlvl model
        Returns:
        an hlvl expression sentence equivalent to the CNF expression
